snippet.textDisplay:
A hauntingly beautiful voice, a wonderful ambience, an eternally mesmerizing smile and top-notch singing. This is what the follow-up to Afreen should have been, not some Coke studio version of an Avril wannabe. Sadly, bollywood music doesnt even come close to what this and Afreen make me go through.
After afreen, this shall become the second most played song on my playlist by the end of the year. Momina Mustehsan, keep singing. You'll forever have me as a fan.

Love from India. ^_^. And a belated Eid mubarak brothers.
